	(text "K1 contactor: J2 low-current switch drives coil + D5 flyback.  K2 bypass: Q1(2N7002 low-side)+Rg/Rgs gate+D6 flyback; MCU drives gate ~500ms after inrush via J9(CTRL).  Bucks U1/U2/U3 EN=always-on(verify pullup), U2=DNP.  U4/K1/K2 need real part numbers.  Provisional F1(BMS)/F4(stepper)/servo-stall/7S."
